sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User / Channel
    participant O as Orchestrator
    participant S as Run State
    participant R as Reasoning Core
    participant G as Governance
    participant T as Tool Runtime

    U->>O: task + identity + constraints
    O->>S: initialize goal, budget, status and trace
    loop bounded by step / time / cost
        O->>S: read current state and observations
        O->>R: decision context + available capabilities
        R-->>O: act / finish / clarify / escalate
        alt action intent
            O->>G: validate identity, permission, risk and budget
            alt action allowed
                G-->>O: allow
                O->>T: execute validated action
                T-->>O: observation / typed error
                O->>S: append observation and trace
            else denied or approval required
                G-->>O: typed control result
                O->>S: record waiting / denied / failed
            end
        else finish candidate
            O->>O: run business acceptance
            O->>S: completed or replan
        else clarification or escalation
            O->>S: record waiting / escalated
        end
    end
    O-->>U: progress / accepted result / failure / handoff
